#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:44
msgid "Deliverability"
msgstr "Uwasilishaji"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:46
msgid ""
"A diagnostic check only — nothing here changes how mail is sent. On ordinary "
"hosting (PHP mail(), no SMTP plugin), mail sent from an address that doesn't "
"match your site's own domain, or from a domain with no SPF/DMARC record at "
"all, is increasingly likely to land in spam or be rejected outright by large "
"mailbox providers. If any row below looks wrong, the most reliable fix is "
"installing an SMTP-sending plugin (WP Mail SMTP, Post SMTP, FluentSMTP, and "
"others all work) configured against a real transactional mail provider, and "
"adding SPF/DMARC records for the domain you send from at your DNS host."
msgstr ""
"Hiki ni ukaguzi wa uchunguzi tu — hakuna kinachobadilisha namna barua "
"zinavyotumwa. Katika huduma ya kawaida ya mwenyeji (PHP mail(), bila "
"programu-jalizi ya SMTP), barua zinazotumwa kutoka kwa anwani isiyolingana "
"na domeni ya tovuti yako, au kutoka kwa domeni isiyo na rekodi ya SPF/DMARC "
"kabisa, zina uwezekano mkubwa zaidi wa kuingia kwenye taka au kukataliwa "
"moja kwa moja na watoa huduma wakubwa wa visanduku vya barua. Ikiwa safu "
"yoyote hapa chini inaonekana si sahihi, suluhisho la kuaminika zaidi ni "
"kusakinisha programu-jalizi ya kutuma SMTP (WP Mail SMTP, Post SMTP, "
"FluentSMTP, na nyinginezo zote hufanya kazi) iliyosanidiwa dhidi ya mtoa "
"huduma halisi wa barua za miamala, na kuongeza rekodi za SPF/DMARC kwa "
"domeni unayotuma kutoka kwake kwenye mwenyeji wako wa DNS."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:52
msgid "From identity"
msgstr "Utambulisho wa kutoka"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:53
msgid "Domain matches site?"
msgstr "Domeni inalingana na tovuti?"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:54
msgid "SPF record"
msgstr "Rekodi ya SPF"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:55
msgid "DMARC record"
msgstr "Rekodi ya DMARC"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:56
msgid "DKIM record"
msgstr "Rekodi ya DKIM"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:57
msgid "Spamhaus DBL"
msgstr "Spamhaus DBL"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:75
msgid "SMTP plugin"
msgstr "Programu-jalizi ya SMTP"

#. translators: %s: detected plugin name, e.g. "WP Mail SMTP"
#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:82
#, php-format
msgid "Detected: %s"
msgstr "Imegunduliwa: %s"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:87
msgid ""
"None of the common SMTP-sending plugins were detected — this site is likely "
"relying on PHP's built-in mail(), which most hosts deliver poorly through."
msgstr ""
"Hakuna hata moja ya programu-jalizi za kawaida za kutuma SMTP iliyogunduliwa "
"— tovuti hii huenda inategemea PHP mail() iliyojengewa ndani, ambayo "
"wapangishaji wengi huiwasilisha vibaya."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:94
msgid ""
"DKIM is best-effort: there's no fixed location for a DKIM record the way SPF "
"and DMARC have, so this only checks a handful of common provider selectors. "
"\"Not found\" here does not mean DKIM isn't configured — only that it isn't "
"under one of the names this check happens to try. If you already know your "
"DKIM is set up correctly (your provider's dashboard confirmed it), trust "
"that over this row."
msgstr ""
"DKIM ni kwa juhudi bora: hakuna eneo maalum la rekodi ya DKIM kama ilivyo "
"kwa SPF na DMARC, kwa hiyo hii huangalia tu vichaguzi vichache vya kawaida "
"vya mtoa huduma. \"Haikupatikana\" hapa haimaanishi DKIM haijasanidiwa — "
"bali haiko chini ya mojawapo ya majina ambayo ukaguzi huu hujaribu. Ikiwa "
"tayari unajua DKIM yako imesanidiwa ipasavyo (dashibodi ya mtoa huduma wako "
"imethibitisha hivyo), amini hilo zaidi ya safu hii."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:100
msgid "Send a real test email to:"
msgstr "Tuma barua pepe ya majaribio halisi kwa:"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:105
msgid ""
"Sends one plain-text email from the same community identity used for review/"
"vote/vouch mail. Reaching your inbox is a good sign; landing in spam or not "
"arriving at all confirms a real deliverability problem regardless of what "
"the checks above say."
msgstr ""
