"Could not send the invitation — check the address and your site's outgoing "
"mail configuration."
msgstr ""
"Haikuweza kutuma mwaliko — angalia anwani na usanidi wa barua zinazotoka wa "
"tovuti yako."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:174
msgid "Test invitation sent — check the inbox you sent it to."
msgstr ""
"Mwaliko wa majaribio umetumwa — angalia kisanduku pokezi ulicholitumia."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:175
msgid ""
"Could not send the test invitation — check the address and your site's "
"outgoing mail configuration."
msgstr ""
"Haikuweza kutuma mwaliko wa majaribio — angalia anwani na usanidi wa barua "
"zinazotoka wa tovuti yako."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:176
msgid ""
"Test email sent — check whether it lands in your inbox or your spam folder."
msgstr ""
"Barua pepe ya majaribio imetumwa — angalia kama inaingia kwenye kisanduku "
"pokezi chako au kwenye folda ya taka."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:178
msgid "Branding preview sent — check the inbox you sent it to."
msgstr "Onyesho la chapa limetumwa — angalia kikasha ulichotumia kulituma."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:179
msgid ""
"Could not send the branding preview — check the address and your site's "
"outgoing mail configuration."
msgstr ""
"Haikuweza kutuma onyesho la chapa — angalia anwani na usanidi wa barua pepe "
"inayoondoka wa tovuti yako."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:180
msgid ""
"Failed recipients reset to pending — they will be retried on the next few "
"cron cycles."
msgstr ""
"Wapokeaji walioshindwa wamewekwa tena kuwa inasubiri — watajaribiwa tena "
"katika mizunguko michache ijayo ya cron."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:181
msgid "No failed recipients to retry for this newsletter."
msgstr "Hakuna wapokeaji walioshindwa wa kujaribu tena kwa jarida hili."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:195
msgid "Art blooming out of oblivion"
msgstr "Sanaa inayochipuka kutoka kwenye usahaulifu"

