msgstr "Rudisha kwenye chaguo-msingi"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:361
msgid ""
"Replaces the text above with the plugin's built-in default — click Save "
"Changes below to keep it."
msgstr ""
"Hubadilisha maandishi yaliyo juu na chaguo-msingi lililojengwa ndani la "
"programu-jalizi — bofya Hifadhi Mabadiliko hapa chini ili kulihifadhi."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:384
