msgstr "Habari %s,"

#. translators: %s: community name
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:399
#, php-format
msgid ""
"One last step before %s can review your application: confirm this is really "
"your email address."
msgstr ""
"Hatua ya mwisho kabla ya %s kuweza kukagua ombi lako: thibitisha kuwa hili "
"kweli ni anwani yako ya barua pepe."

#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:407
msgid ""
"If you didn't apply, simply ignore this email — nothing happens until this "
"link is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Kama hukuomba, pumzika tu na barua pepe hii — hakuna kinachotokea mpaka "
"kiungo hiki kibonyezwe."

#. translators: %s: community name
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:446
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Thank you for applying to %s. Your application has been received and is now "
"awaiting review by an admin."
msgstr ""
"Asante kwa kutuma ombi lako kwa %s. Ombi lako limepokelewa na sasa "
"linasubiri ukaguzi wa msimamizi."

#. translators: %s: community name
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:451
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Thank you for applying to %s. Your application has been received and is now "
"open for community review."
msgstr ""
"Asante kwa kuomba kujiunga na %s. Ombi lako limepokelewa na sasa liko wazi "
"kwa ukaguzi wa jamii."

#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:458
msgid ""
"There is no fixed deadline — we will let you know the outcome by email as "
"soon as a decision is made."
msgstr ""
"Hakuna muda wa mwisho ulioainishwa — tutakujulisha matokeo kwa barua pepe "
"mara tu uamuzi utakapofanywa."

#. translators: %d: number of days
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:461
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The community has %d days to vote. We will let you know the outcome by email."
msgstr ""
"Jamii ina siku %d za kupiga kura. Tutakujulisha matokeo kupitia barua pepe."

#. translators: 1: site name, 2: applicant display name
