"Agnosis, au muulize msimamizi."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:539
msgid ""
"Your biography, statement, and portfolio link were erased. Your email "
"address was kept on file — your account is currently banned, and it's the "
"only way this site can continue to enforce that."
msgstr ""
"Wasifu wako, taarifa, na kiungo cha jalada la kazi vilifutwa. Anwani yako ya "
"barua pepe ilibaki kwenye kumbukumbu — akaunti yako kwa sasa imepigwa "
"marufuku, na hicho ndicho kigezo pekee kinachoruhusu tovuti hii kuendelea "
"kutekeleza hilo."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:613 includes/Core/Privacy.php:685
msgid "[message removed]"
msgstr "[ujumbe umeondolewa]"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:624
msgid ""
"Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept "
"as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it "
"would silently change a settled decision."
msgstr ""
"Ujumbe wa vouch ulioandika ulifichuliwa. Kura za utawala ulizopiga "
"zilihifadhiwa jinsi zilivyo — kura ni rekodi ya jamii, si data binafsi, na "
"kuiondoa kungebadilisha kimya kimya uamuzi uliokwisha fikiwa."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:667
msgid ""
"Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts "
"were kept for statistics."
msgstr ""
"Rekodi za awali za uwasilishaji wa jarida zilifichwa utambulisho; hesabu za "
"uwasilishaji kwa kila toleo ziliwekwa kwa ajili ya takwimu."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:728
msgid ""
"Transaction (donation/sale) records were kept in full — financial records "
"are subject to a legal retention obligation and are exempt from erasure "
"under GDPR Art. 17(3)(b)."
msgstr ""
"Rekodi za miamala (michango/uuzaji) zilihifadhiwa kikamilifu — rekodi za "
"kifedha ziko chini ya wajibu wa kisheria wa kuhifadhiwa na hazina msamaha wa "
"kufutwa chini ya GDPR Art. 17(3)(b)."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:766
msgid ""
"Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting "
"point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site's "
"actual configuration before publishing."
msgstr ""
"Agnosis ni programu-jalizi ya uchapishaji wa sanaa iliyounganishwa kwa "
"mtandao wa fediverse. Ifuatayo ni sehemu ya kuanzia ya kuelezea kile "
"inachokusanya — kagua na urekebishe ili ilingane na usanidi halisi wa tovuti "
"yako kabla ya kuchapisha."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:767
msgid "What personal data we collect and why"
msgstr "Tunaokusanya data gani binafsi na kwa nini"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:768
msgid ""
"When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, "
"biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching "
"process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of "
"that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and "
"reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through "
"their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, "
"your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues."
msgstr ""
"Unapotuma ombi la kujiunga, tunahifadhi anwani yako ya barua pepe, jina la "
"kuonyesha, wasifu, taarifa, na kiungo cha jalada la kazi ili kuendesha "
"mchakato wa uthibitishaji wa jamii. Unapotutumia kazi ya sanaa, wasifu, au "
"tukio kwa barua pepe, maudhui ya barua hiyo (ikiwemo anwani yako) "
"huhifadhiwa wakati yanashughulikiwa na kukaguliwa. Unapojiandikisha kwa "
"jarida letu au kumwandikia msanii kupitia fomu yake ya mawasiliano, "
"tunahifadhi anwani yako ya barua pepe (na, kwa ujumbe wa mawasiliano, anwani "
"yako ya IP) ili kuwasilisha ujumbe huo au kukutumia matoleo ya baadaye."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:769
msgid "Who we share it with"
msgstr "Tunashiriki na nani"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:770
msgid ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."
msgstr ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:771
msgid "How long we retain your data"
msgstr "Tunahifadhi data yako kwa muda gani"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:772
msgid ""
"Retention varies by data type; see this site's administrator for specifics. "
"You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described "
"above at any time using this site's standard WordPress data request tools."
msgstr ""
"Muda wa kuhifadhi hutofautiana kulingana na aina ya data; muulize msimamizi "
"wa tovuti hii kwa maelezo mahususi. Unaweza kuomba nakala ya, au ufutaji wa, "
"data binafsi iliyoelezwa hapo juu wakati wowote kwa kutumia zana za kawaida "
"za WordPress za maombi ya data za tovuti hii."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:800
msgid ""
"Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. "
"Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this "
"cannot be fully undone later."
msgstr ""
"Maandishi na picha zilizowasilishwa zinaweza kuchakatwa na mtoa huduma wa AI "
"wa nje. Machapisho yaliyoidhinishwa huchapishwa hadharani na kushirikiwa "
"kote katika Fediverse — hili haliwezi kufutwa kikamilifu baadaye."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:801
msgid ""
"Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being "
"sent to the artist."
msgstr ""
"Ujumbe wako unaweza kukaguliwa na kichujio cha maudhui cha kiotomatiki kabla "
"ya kutumwa kwa msanii."

