msgstr "Tupa"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1029
msgid "Want to tweak the title, text or tags before publishing?"
msgstr "Unataka kurekebisha kichwa, maandishi au lebo kabla ya kuchapisha?"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1031
msgid "Open your submissions page →"
msgstr "Fungua ukurasa wako wa mawasilisho →"

#. translators: %d is the number of days the review link stays valid — configurable under Settings, Behavior tab
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1041
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d day. Your submission stays "
"as a draft until you decide."
msgid_plural ""
"The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d days. Your submission stays "
"as a draft until you decide."
msgstr[0] ""
"Viungo vya Chapisha na Tupa vilivyo hapo juu vinaisha baada ya siku %d moja. "
"Uwasilishaji wako unabaki kama rasimu mpaka uamue."
msgstr[1] ""
"Viungo vya Chapisha na Tupa vilivyo hapo juu vinaisha baada ya siku %d. "
"Uwasilishaji wako unabaki kama rasimu mpaka uamue."

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1147
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] We couldn't process your submission"
msgstr "[%s] Hatukuweza kuchakata uwasilishaji wako"

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1203
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] We couldn't find a photo in your email"
msgstr "[%s] Hatukuweza kupata picha katika barua pepe yako"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1239
msgid ""
"We received your email, but couldn't process a usable photo, audio, or video "
"file from it — so nothing was published. This can happen when an image is "
"pasted or inserted inline rather than added as a proper attachment, or when "
"a file arrives in a format this server can't convert (for example, an iPhone "
"photo saved in HEIC/HEIF format)."
msgstr ""
"Tulipokea barua pepe yako, lakini hatukuweza kuchakata faili ya picha, "
"sauti, au video inayoweza kutumika kutoka humo — kwa hiyo hakuna "
"kilichochapishwa. Hii inaweza kutokea picha inapobandikwa au kuingizwa ndani "
"ya ujumbe badala ya kuambatishwa ipasavyo, au faili inapofika katika umbizo "
"ambalo seva hii haiwezi kubadilisha (kwa mfano, picha ya iPhone "
"iliyohifadhiwa katika umbizo la HEIC/HEIF)."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1243
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1349
msgid "To resend correctly:"
msgstr "Ili kutuma tena kwa usahihi:"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1245
msgid ""
"Use your mail app's \"Attach file\" (usually a paperclip icon) rather than "
"\"Insert photo\" or pasting the image directly into the message body."
msgstr ""
"Tumia \"Ambatisha faili\" ya programu yako ya barua (kwa kawaida ikoni ya "
"klipu ya karatasi) badala ya \"Ingiza picha\" au kubandika picha moja kwa "
"moja kwenye sehemu ya ujumbe."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1246
msgid ""
"If your photo was taken on an iPhone, try switching Settings → Camera → "
"Formats to \"Most Compatible\" before taking or sending it, or use \"Options"
"\" in Mail to send it as a JPEG."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa picha yako ilipigwa kwa iPhone, jaribu kubadilisha Mipangilio → Kamera "
"→ Miundo kuwa \"Inaoana zaidi\" kabla ya kuipiga au kuituma, au tumia "
"\"Chaguo\" katika Mail kuituma kama JPEG."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1247
msgid ""
"Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF, or HEIC/HEIF for images; MP3, "
"WAV, M4A, OGG, or FLAC for audio; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG, or MPEG for "
"video."
msgstr ""
"Miundo inayotumika: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF, au HEIC/HEIF kwa picha; MP3, "
"WAV, M4A, OGG, au FLAC kwa sauti; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG, au MPEG kwa "
"video."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1252
msgid ""
"Once it's properly attached, just send it to the same address again — we'll "
"pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Mara itakapokuwa imeambatishwa ipasavyo, itume tu tena kwenye anwani ileile "
"— tutaipata kiotomatiki."

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1309
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] We couldn't process that email"
msgstr "[%s] Hatukuweza kuchakata barua pepe hiyo"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1345
msgid ""
"We received your email, but it looked like a reply or a forwarded message — "
"carrying quoted text from an earlier email. We looked for your own original "
"text or an attachment above the quoted part, but couldn't find anything to "
"work with, so nothing was published."
msgstr ""
"Tulipokea barua pepe yako, lakini ilionekana kama jibu au ujumbe uliotumwa "
"mbele — ikiwa na maandishi yaliyotajwa moja kwa moja kutoka kwa barua pepe "
"ya awali. Tulitafuta maandishi yako ya asili au kiambatisho juu ya sehemu "
"iliyotajwa, lakini hatukupata chochote cha kufanyia kazi, kwa hiyo hakuna "
"kilichochapishwa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1351
msgid ""
"Start a brand new message rather than replying to or forwarding a previous "
"one — this is always the most reliable way to reach us."
msgstr ""
"Anza ujumbe mpya kabisa badala ya kujibu au kutuma mbele ujumbe wa awali — "
"hili daima ndilo njia ya kuaminika zaidi ya kutufikia."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1352
msgid ""
"Give it a plain subject line — not one starting with \"Re:\" or containing "
"\"[Agnosis]\"."
msgstr "Weka kichwa rahisi — kisichoanza na \"Re:\" au chenye \"[Agnosis]\"."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1353
msgid ""
"Make sure the body only contains your own, original text and attachment — no "
"quoted or forwarded content from an earlier message."
msgstr ""
"Hakikisha mwili una maandishi yako mwenyewe ya asili na kiambatisho tu — "
"hakuna yaliyotajwa moja kwa moja au yaliyotumwa mbele kutoka kwa ujumbe wa "
"awali."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1358
msgid ""
"Once it's a fresh, original message, just send it to the same address again "
"— we'll pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Mara tu itakapokuwa ujumbe mpya kabisa, wa asili, utume tena kwenye anwani "
"ile ile — tutajichukua kiotomatiki."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1399
msgid ""
"The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a "
"large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side."
msgstr ""
"Picha ni nyeusi sana kiasi kwamba haiwezi kuonyesha kazi yako ya sanaa kwa "
"uwazi. Jaribu kupiga picha karibu na dirisha kubwa wakati wa mchana, au "
"tumia taa laini ukiielekeza kwenye kazi kutoka upande."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1400
msgid ""
"The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window "
"in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side."
msgstr ""
"Picha imepigwa kwa mwanga hafifu sana (ni nyeusi kupita kiasi). Jaribu "
"kupiga picha karibu na dirisha kubwa wakati wa mchana, au tumia taa laini "
"ukiielekeza kwenye kazi kutoka upande."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1401
msgid ""
"The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or "
"flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best."
msgstr ""
"Picha imepigwa kwa mwanga mwingi kupita kiasi (ni ang’avu sana / imefutika). "
"Epuka jua la moja kwa moja au flash iliyolengwa moja kwa moja kwenye kazi ya "
"sanaa — mwanga ulioenezwa au usio wa moja kwa moja hufanya kazi vizuri zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1402
msgid ""
"The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — "
"diffuse light or shade gives more even tones."
msgstr ""
"Picha ni ang’avu sana au imefutika. Epuka jua la moja kwa moja au flash — "
"mwanga uliotawanyika au kivuli hutoa tani zilizo sawa zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1403
msgid ""
"There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas "
"slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface."
msgstr ""
"Kuna mng’ao au miale ya mwanga mkali kwenye kazi ya sanaa. Pindua turubai "
"kidogo au piga picha kwa pembe ili kuondoa mwangaza unaoakisiwa kutoka "
"kwenye uso."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1404
msgid ""
"There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or "
"change your angle to eliminate it."
msgstr ""
"Kuna mwanga unaoakisiwa kwenye uso wa kazi ya sanaa. Pindua turubai kidogo "
"au badilisha pembe yako ili kuuondoa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1406
msgid ""
"The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the "
"self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus "
"locks on it."
msgstr ""
"Picha imefifia. Weka simu au kamera yako juu ya uso thabiti, tumia kipima "
"muda cha kujipiga, na hakikisha kazi ya sanaa inajaza sehemu kubwa ya fremu "
"ili autofocus ifungamane nayo."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1407
msgid ""
"The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before "
"shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still."
msgstr ""
"Picha haiko kwenye focus. Gusa kazi ya sanaa kwenye skrini ya simu yako "
"kabla ya kupiga picha ili kuhakikisha autofocus inafungamana nayo, na "
"ushikilie kamera bila kusogea."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1408
msgid ""
"There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the "
"shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake."
msgstr ""
"Kuna ukungu wa mwendo. Shikilia kamera bila kusogea kabisa au tumia tripod; "
"bonyeza shutter kwa upole au tumia kipima muda cha kujipiga ili kuepuka "
"mtikisiko."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1409
msgid ""
"Camera shake is visible. Use a tripod or rest the camera on a flat surface "
"and use the self-timer to avoid movement when pressing the shutter."
msgstr ""
"Mtikisiko wa kamera unaonekana. Tumia tripod au weka kamera juu ya uso "
"tambarare na tumia kipima muda cha kujipiga ili kuepuka kusogea unapobonyeza "
"shutter."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1411
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and make sure you're close enough that the artwork fills the frame."
msgstr ""
"Uazimio wa picha ni mdogo sana. Tumia mpangilio wa ubora wa juu zaidi kwenye "
"simu yako na hakikisha uko karibu vya kutosha ili kazi ya sanaa ijaze fremu."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1412
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and fill the frame with the artwork."
msgstr ""
"Uazimio wa picha ni mdogo sana. Tumia mpangilio wa ubora wa juu zaidi kwenye "
"simu yako na ijaze fremu kwa kazi ya sanaa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1413
msgid ""
"The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting "
"on your camera."
msgstr ""
"Picha ina vizuizi vya pikseli. Piga kutoka karibu zaidi au tumia mpangilio "
"wa uazimio wa juu zaidi kwenye kamera yako."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1415
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1416
msgid ""
"The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your "
"phone's Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors."
msgstr ""
"Picha ina mabadiliko makubwa ya rangi. Piga chini ya mwanga wa asili usio na "
"rangi au tumia mpangilio wa Auto White Balance wa simu yako kwa rangi zilizo "
"sahihi zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1417
msgid ""
"The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch "
"your phone's white balance to Daylight / Cloudy."
msgstr ""
"Picha inaonekana ya manjano sana au ya joto kupita kiasi. Piga chini ya "
"mwanga wa asili wa mchana au badilisha white balance ya simu yako kuwa "
"Daylight / Cloudy."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1418
msgid ""
"The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural "
"light source or adjust your camera's white balance."
msgstr ""
"Picha ina kivuli cha buluu baridi. Hamisha kazi ya sanaa hadi kwenye chanzo "
"cha mwanga chenye joto zaidi na cha asili zaidi au rekebisha white balance "
"ya kamera yako."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1420
msgid ""
"Part of the artwork appears to be cropped out of the frame. Step back and "
"make sure the entire work is visible before shooting."
msgstr ""
"Sehemu ya kazi ya sanaa inaonekana imekatwa kutoka kwenye fremu. Sogea nyuma "
"na hakikisha kazi nzima inaonekana kabla ya kupiga picha."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1421
msgid ""
"The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight "
"on, with the camera parallel to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Kazi ya sanaa imepigwa picha kwa pembe, na kusababisha upotoshaji. Piga "
"picha moja kwa moja, huku kamera ikiwa sambamba na turubai."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1422
msgid ""
"The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in "
"front of the artwork, parallel to its surface."
msgstr ""
"Kazi ya sanaa inaonekana imepotoshwa au imepinda. Weka kamera yako moja kwa "
"moja mbele ya kazi ya sanaa, sambamba na uso wake."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1423
msgid ""
"There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source "
"or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface."
msgstr ""
"Kuna kivuli kinachopita juu ya sehemu ya kazi ya sanaa. Rekebisha tena "
"chanzo chako cha mwanga au isogeze kazi ya sanaa ili hakuna vivuli "
"vinavyotua juu ya uso."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1473
msgid ""
"We received your submission, but unfortunately the photo quality is too low "
"for us to show your artwork clearly. We didn't publish it — but please don't "
"be discouraged! A simple retake is usually all it takes."
msgstr ""
"Tumepokea uwasilishaji wako, lakini kwa bahati mbaya ubora wa picha ni mdogo "
"sana kiasi kwamba hatuwezi kuonyesha kazi yako ya sanaa kwa uwazi. "
"Hatukuiweka — lakini tafadhali usivunjike moyo! Kupiga tena picha mara moja "
"kwa kawaida kunatosha."

#. translators: %d: quality score out of 10
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1482
#, php-format
msgid "📷 Photo quality score: %d / 10"
msgstr "📷 Alama ya ubora wa picha: %d / 10"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1488
msgid "Here's what our AI detected and how to fix it:"
msgstr "Haya ndiyo AI yetu iligundua na jinsi ya kuyarekebisha:"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1495
msgid ""
"The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork "
"clearly."
msgstr ""
"Ubora wa jumla wa picha ulikuwa mdogo sana kwa AI yetu kuchakata kazi ya "
"sanaa kwa uwazi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1501
msgid "💡 Quick tips for a great artwork photo"
msgstr "💡 Vidokezo vya haraka kwa picha nzuri ya kazi ya sanaa"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1503
msgid ""
"Use natural light — position the artwork near a window on a cloudy day for "
"even, soft light."
msgstr ""
"Tumia mwanga wa asili — weka kazi ya sanaa karibu na dirisha siku ya mawingu "
"kwa mwanga laini na sawa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1504
msgid ""
"Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid "
"perspective distortion."
msgstr ""
"Piga picha moja kwa moja — shikilia simu yako sambamba na turubai ili "
"kuepuka upotoshaji wa mtazamo."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1505
msgid ""
"Fill the frame — let the artwork take up most of the shot; crop out "
"distracting backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"Jaza fremu — acha kazi ya sanaa ichukue sehemu kubwa ya picha; kata "
"mandharinyuma yanayokengeusha."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1506
msgid ""
"Hold still — tap the artwork on your screen to focus, then press the shutter "
"gently or use a self-timer."
msgstr ""
"Shikilia bila kusogea — gusa kazi ya sanaa kwenye skrini yako ili kufocus, "
"kisha bonyeza shutter kwa upole au tumia kipima muda cha kujipiga."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1511
msgid ""
"Once you have a clearer photo, just email it to the same address as before — "
"we'll pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ukishapata picha iliyo wazi zaidi, itume tu kwa barua pepe kwenye anwani "
"ileile kama hapo awali — tutaichukua kiotomatiki."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1516
msgid ""
"Your previous submission is saved in your submissions page in case you want "
"to review what was sent."
msgstr ""
"Uwasilishaji wako wa awali umehifadhiwa kwenye ukurasa wako wa uwasilishaji "
"iwapo ungependa kupitia ulichotuma."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1518
msgid "View submissions →"
msgstr "Tazama uwasilishaji →"

